data.description: Welcome HOME to this 2022  2-Story located in Promontory! Upon entering this  bright spacious move-in ready  house you'll see beautiful hardwood floors that lead into the open main floor great room, dining & kitchen.  Large windows with southern exposure shows off the large kitchen with oversized island, lots of cabinet and countertop space. Walk out onto the oversized deck that brings you into a nice size backyard. Upstairs find 4 roomy bedrooms including the huge primary suite that features a 5 pc. luxury bathroom with a soaker tub and oversized shower and large walk in closet. The second floor laundry is an excellent way to save time and make laundering easier. The oversized drywalled garage has enough square footage for 3 cars.  Located one block from the playground.  Has easy access to  Hwy 34. Are you looking for a mortgage at 5.25%? Then contact agent about assuming the current Sellers FHA loan with 8% down.
